com.motorola.mod

Class ModDevice.Interface

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.motorola.mod.ModDevice.Interface
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable, ModDevice.InterfaceInfo
    Enclosing class:
    ModDevice

    public static class ModDevice.Interface
extends Object
implements ModDevice.InterfaceInfo
    An interface descriptor describes an access point for a module to the UniPro network; the difference between this class vs. ModDevice.InterfaceInfo is that, an instance of this class means there is an actual interface being created underneath.
